*--------------------------------( Misc: Idea )------------------------------*

   Type:        command
   Usage:       idea <text>
                
   Description: This is an out of character command. If you have an idea
		to make the MUD better describe it.
                
   Example:     idea the dragon should use fire spells
                    
*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*
 See also: 'bug', 'typo', 'ooc'
